<p>Wednesday 20/6/17<br/>Wrote to the General, raining Field day postponed.<br/>Thursday 21/6/17<br/>Raining, went to see Corps Line, had dinner with 17th then visited the nurses at 3rd C.C.S. [Casualty Clearing Station]<br/>Friday 22/6/17<br/>Field Day carried out, raining heavily.<br/>Saturday 23/6/17<br/>Remained in bed all day with a touch of Malaria. Runner shot at night.<br/>Sunday 24/6/17<br/>Church Parade, played Officers match against 28th cricket, we won, made a score.</p>
